Header = Von Cedric

Titel = Belgische Waffeln

Tags = breakfast, quick bread

Zutaten =
2  Egg
1 cup Butter
0.5 cup Sugar
1.5 cup Milk
2 tsp Vanilla
2 cup Flour
1 tbsp Baking Powder

Zubereitung =
Separate eggs. Whip egg whites until stiff peaks form. Set asside.
Melt butter, and combine with sugar. Add egg yokes and mix well.
Add milk and vanilla and mix well.
Add flour and sugar until just combined.
Fold in egg whites.
Follow instructions on waffle maker or add .5 cup of batter to waffle iron and cook for 4 minutes.


Gewonne Menge = 10 waffles